							<a href="http://goperu.about.com/od/machupicchuincatrail/fl/Inca-Trail-Age-Restrictions.htm" data-component="expertLandingPageRecentArticles" data-source="ArticleSite_Latest" data-type="article.heading" data-ordinal="11">Are There Any Inca Trail Age Restrictions?</a>
						</h5>
							<a href="http://goperu.about.com/od/machupicchuincatrail/fl/Inca-Trail-Age-Restrictions.htm" data-component="expertLandingPageRecentArticles" data-source="ArticleSite_Latest" data-type="article.blurb" data-ordinal="11" class="article-blurb">There are no official age restrictions for trekking the Inca Trail to Machu Picchu, but some tour operators do have their own age limits.</a>
						<div><div class="share-options-container open-right with-msg">
<div class="share-btns share-options popout"
data-url="http://goperu.about.com/od/machupicchuincatrail/fl/Inca-Trail-Age-Restrictions.htm"
data-social-title="Are There Any Inca Trail Age Restrictions?"
data-description="There are no official age restrictions for trekking the Inca Trail to Machu Picchu, but some tour operators do have their own age limits."
data-social-image="http://f.tqn.com/y/goperu/1/S/A/D/-/-/trek_inca_trail_age_limits.jpg">
